<h3>Methodology</h3>
<p>NetBlocks diffscans, which map the IP address space of a country in real time, show internet connectivity levels and corresponding outages. Purposeful internet outages may have a distinct network pattern used by NetBlocks to determine and attribute the root cause of an outage, a process known as <em>attribution</em> which follows <em>detection</em> and <em>classification</em> stages.</p>

